  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(grad \\, div\\,\\vec{E}\\right)_x = \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}\\left(\\frac{\\partial E_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} +  i\\,K_z E_z(x, y)\\right)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z} \\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$"
