  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$${k'_z}^2=\\left(k_z + i\\,s_z \\right)^2 = k_z^2 - s_z^2 + 2\\,i\\,k_z\\,s_z$$"
