   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} - {k'_z}^2\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y)  + \\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{y}}{\\partial x}} + \\mu'_{yz} \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}- \\left(grad\\,div\\,\\vec{E}\\right)_z = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} - {k'_z}^2\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y)  = + \\left(grad\\,div\\,\\vec{E}\\right)_z - \\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{y}}{\\partial x}} - \\mu'_{yz} \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} - {k'_z}^2\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y)  = \\left(i \\,k'_z\\,\\frac{\\partial E_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} -\\,{k'_z}^2 E_z(x, y)\\right) - \\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{y}}{\\partial x}} - \\mu'_{yz} \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} - {k'_z}^2\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y) = \\left(i \\,k'_z\\,\\frac{\\partial E_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} -\\,{k'_z}^2 E_z(x, y)\\right)-\\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{y}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Таким образом получено волновое уравнение"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y)  = \\left(i \\,k'_z\\,\\frac{\\partial E_x(x, y)}{\\partial x}\\right) - \\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{y}}{\\partial x}} - \\mu'_{yz} \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y) = \\left(i \\,k'_z\\,\\frac{\\partial E_x(x, y)}{\\partial x}\\right)-\\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{y}}{\\partial x}}$$"
