  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Рассмотрим TM волну для которой $H_z = 0$. \n",
    "\n",
    "Для этой волны учитывая что $K_z = {k'_z}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{{k'_z} c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right) H_{y} = -\\frac{1}{{k'_z}}{\\frac {\\partial E_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ \\left(\\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega{\\mu'}_{yy}} - \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{{k'_z}c} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right) E_x = \\frac{c}{\\omega{\\mu'}_{yy}}{\\frac {\\partial E_{z}}{\\partial x}} $$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "откуда, выражая поперечные компоненты поля,"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ H_{y} = -\\frac{1}{{k'_z} \\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{{k'_z} c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial E_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$  E_x = \\frac{c}{\\omega{\\mu'}_{yy}\\left(\\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega{\\mu'}_{yy}} - \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{{k'_z}c} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial E_{z}}{\\partial x}} $$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "упрощая"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ H_{y} = -\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z}^2 c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial E_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$  E_x = \\frac{c}{\\left({i {k'_z} c} - \\frac{i\\,\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial E_{z}}{\\partial x}} $$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "дифференцируя по x"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ \\frac{\\partial H_{y}}{\\partial x} = -\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z}^2 c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 E_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial E_x}{\\partial x} = \\frac{1}{\\left({i {k'_z}} - \\frac{i\\,\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 E_{z}}{\\partial x^2}} $$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "подставляя в волновое уравнение"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y)  = \\left(i \\,k'_z\\,\\frac{\\partial E_x(x, y)}{\\partial x}\\right) - \\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{y}}{\\partial x}} - \\mu'_{yz} \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y) = \\left(i \\,k'_z\\,\\frac{\\partial E_x(x, y)}{\\partial x}\\right)-\\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial H_{y}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y) = \\left(\\frac{k'_z}{\\left({ {k'_z}} - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 E_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}\\right)+\\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, \\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z}^2 c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 E_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y) = \\left(\\frac{k'_z}{\\left({ {k'_z}} - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 E_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}\\right)+ \\frac{\\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)}{\\left({\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{{k'_z}^2 c^2}{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 E_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(1 - \\frac{k'_z}{\\left({ {k'_z}} - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)} - \\frac{\\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)}{\\left({\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{{k'_z}^2 c^2}{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)}\\right)\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\frac{ \\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}}{\\left(1 - \\frac{k'_z}{\\left({ {k'_z}} - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)} - \\frac{\\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)}{\\left({\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{{k'_z}^2 c^2}{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)}\\right)}\\,{E_z}(x,y) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$K_{x,TM}^2 = \\frac{ \\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}}{\\left(1 - \\frac{k'_z}{\\left({ {k'_z}} - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)} - \\frac{\\left(\\mu'_{yy}-\\mu'_{xx}\\right)}{\\left({\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{{k'_z}^2 c^2}{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)}\\right)}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + K_x^2\\,{E_z}(x,y) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Решение этого дифференциального уравнения для TM волны"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$${C_{0}} e^{i\\,K_x x} + {C_{1}} e^{-i\\, K_x x}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "В случае если $\\mu'_{yy}=\\mu'_{xx}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\frac{ \\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}}{\\left(1 - \\frac{k'_z}{\\left({ {k'_z}} - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)} \\right)}\\,{E_z}(x,y) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left({ {k'_z}} - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)\\frac{ \\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}}{\\left(\\left({ {k'_z}} - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right) - k'_z \\right)}\\,{E_z}(x,y) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left({ {k'_z}} - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} \\right)\\frac{ \\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz} \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2}}{ - \\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} }\\,{E_z}(x,y) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\frac{\\omega^2}{{k'_z}c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} - { {k'_z}} \\right)\\frac{ \\mu'_{xx}\\epsilon'_{zz}}{ \\frac{1}{{k'_z}} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} }\\,{E_z}(x,y) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{xx} - { {k'_z}^2} \\right)\\frac{ \\epsilon'_{zz}}{ {\\epsilon'}_{xx} }\\,{E_z}(x,y) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{E_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} {\\mu'}_{yy} {\\epsilon'}_{zz} - { {k'_z}^2} \\frac{ \\epsilon'_{zz}}{ {\\epsilon'}_{xx} }\\right)\\,{E_z}(x,y) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Теперь начинаем вывод волнового уравнения для поля Н с записи первой пары уравнений Максвелла"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{E} = -\\frac{1}{c}\\frac{\\partial \\vec B}{\\partial t} - \\frac{4\\pi}{c}\\vec j_m = \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c}\\mu'\\,\\vec{H}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{H} = \\frac{1}{c}\\frac{\\partial \\vec D}{\\partial t} + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec j_e  + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec {{j_e}^{ext}}$$\n",
    "\n",
    " $j_e$ - ток проводимости определяемый законом Ома $\\vec j_e = \\sigma_e \\vec E$\n",
    " \n",
    " ${{j_e}^{ext}}$ - внешний ток возбуждения резонатора, не входящий в формулу закона Ома, потому что он не определяется внутренним электрическим полем резонатора, а определяется внешним генератором возбуждения\n",
    " \n",
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{H} = \\frac{1}{c}\\frac{\\partial \\left(\\epsilon \\vec E\\right)}{\\partial t} + \\sigma_e \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec E  + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec {{j_e}^{ext}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "для проводящего металла с потерями ищем решение в виде\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\vec{E} = \\vec{E}(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,k_z\\,z}\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega'\\,t}$$\n",
    "$$\\vec{E} = \\vec{E_0}(x, y, z)\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega'\\,t}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\vec{H} = \\vec{H_0}(x, y, z)\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega'\\,t}$$\n",
    "в котором частота комплексна $\\omega' = \\omega_{re} - i\\,\\omega_{im}$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\vec{E} = \\vec{E}(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,k_z\\,z}\\,e^{-i\\,(\\omega_{re} - i\\,\\omega_{im})\\,t}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\vec{E} = \\vec{E}(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,k_z\\,z}\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega_{re}\\,t}\\,\\cdot\\,e^{-\\omega_{im}\\,t}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\vec{E} = \\vec{E_0}(x, y, z)\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega_{re}\\,t}\\,\\cdot\\,e^{-\\omega_{im}\\,t}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "внешний ток возбуждения\n",
    "$$\\vec{{{j_e}^{ext}}} = \\vec{{{j_e}^{ext}}_0}(x, y, z)\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$\n",
    "в котором частота действительна, ибо внешний ток возбуждения не затухает во времени\n",
    "\n",
    "но вопрос в том, что поля E и H в стационарном ржиме тоже перестанут затухать во времени при наличии внешнего тока возбуждения, но без наличия тока возбуждения они будут затухать. Отсюда противоречие и вопрос - зачем нужна комплексная частота в расчёте резонатора с внешним возбуждением в стационароном режиме?\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{H_0}\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega'\\,t} = \\frac{1}{c}\\frac{\\partial \\left(\\epsilon \\vec E_0\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega'\\,t}\\right)}{\\partial t} + \\sigma_e \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec E_0\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega'\\,t}  + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec {{j_e}^{ext}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "я запишу два уравнения для ротора магнитного поля\n",
    "\n",
    "первое для нестационарного случая затухания полей в резонаторе в отсутствие подкачки внешним током, с комплексной частотой $\\omega'$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{H_0}\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega'\\,t} = \\frac{1}{c}\\frac{\\partial \\left(\\epsilon \\vec E_0\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega'\\,t}\\right)}{\\partial t} + \\sigma_e \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec E_0\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega'\\,t}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "второе для стационарного случая установившегося режима, когда затухание в стенках резонатора за счёт потерь полностью компенсируется подкачкой энергии внешним током подкачки - с действительной частотой $\\omega$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{H_0}\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t} = \\frac{1}{c}\\frac{\\partial \\left(\\epsilon \\vec E_0\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}\\right)}{\\partial t} + \\sigma_e \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec E_0\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}  + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec {{j_e}^{ext}}_0\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "нестационарное затухающее уравнение с комплексной частотой $\\omega'$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{H_0} = - \\frac{i\\,\\omega'}{c} \\epsilon \\vec{E_0} + \\sigma_e \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec E_0$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{H_0} = - \\frac{i\\,\\omega'}{c} \\epsilon' \\vec{E_0}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "где комплексная диэлектрическая проницаемость $\\epsilon' = \\epsilon + \\frac{4\\pi\\,\\sigma}{\\omega'}\\,i$ включает также и комплексную частоту $\\omega'$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "стационарное уравнение с источником возбуждения с действительной частотой $\\omega$ (все переходные процессы уже устаканились)\n",
    "\n",
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{H_0} = - \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\epsilon \\vec{E_0} + \\sigma_e \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec E_0  + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec {{j_e}^{ext}}_0$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{H_0} = - \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\epsilon' \\vec{E_0} + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\vec {{j_e}^{ext}}_0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "где теперь комплексная диэлектрическая проницаемость $\\epsilon' = \\epsilon + \\frac{4\\pi\\,\\sigma}{\\omega}\\,i$ включает действительную частоту  $\\omega$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "произведём преобразования со вторым уравнением Максвелла"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Применяя ко второму уравнению Максвелла операцию ротора\n",
    "\n",
    "$$rot \\, rot\\,\\vec{H} = - \\frac{i\\,\\omega'}{c} rot \\left( \\epsilon' \\vec E\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "и\n",
    "\n",
    "$$rot \\, rot\\,\\vec{H} = - \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} rot \\left( \\epsilon' \\vec E\\right) + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} rot \\left( \\vec {{j_e}^{ext}} \\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "при условии диагональности тензора диэлектрической проницаемости"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ rot \\left( \\epsilon'  \\vec E\\right) =\n",
    "\\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{zz} E_{z}\\right)}{\\partial y}}-{\\frac {\\partial\\left( \\epsilon'_{yy} E_{y}\\right)}{\\partial z}}\\right)\\mathbf {i} +\\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx} E_{x}\\right)}{\\partial z}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{zz} E_{z}\\right)}{\\partial x}}\\right)\\mathbf {j} +\\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{yy} E_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx} E_{x}\\right)}{\\partial y}}\\right)\\mathbf {k}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    " $$\\frac{4\\pi}{c} rot \\left( \\vec {{j_e}^{ext}} \\right) = \\frac{4\\pi}{c}\\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left({{j_e}^{ext}}_{z}\\right)}{\\partial y}}-{\\frac {\\partial\\left( {{j_e}^{ext}}_{y}\\right)}{\\partial z}}\\right)\\mathbf {i} +\\frac{4\\pi}{c}\\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left({{j_e}^{ext}}_{x}\\right)}{\\partial z}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left({{j_e}^{ext}}_{z}\\right)}{\\partial x}}\\right)\\mathbf {j} +\\frac{4\\pi}{c}\\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left({{j_e}^{ext}}_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left({{j_e}^{ext}}_{x}\\right)}{\\partial y}}\\right)\\mathbf {k}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Поскольку нам нужно получить дифференциальное уравнение для продольной (z) компоненты поля (ибо поперечные компоненты поля выше уже удалось выразить через продольные, мы далее пишем"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": []
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "\n",
    "$$\\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z =  -\\frac{i\\,\\omega'}{c} \\, \\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}E_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx} E_{x}\\right)}{\\partial y}}\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z =  -\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, \\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}E_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx} E_{x}\\right)}{\\partial y}}\\right) + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\, \\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\vec {{j_e}^{ext}}_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\vec {{j_e}^{ext}}_{x}\\right)}{\\partial y}}\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Поскольку внешний ток имеет только лишь игрековую компоненту\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z =  -\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, \\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}E_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx} E_{x}\\right)}{\\partial y}}\\right) + \\frac{4\\pi}{c} \\, \\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\vec {{j_e}^{ext}}_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}}\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = - \\frac{i\\,\\omega'}{c} \\, \\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}-\\epsilon'_{xx}+\\epsilon'_{xx}\\right)E_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx} E_{x}\\right)}{\\partial y}}\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = - \\frac{i\\,\\omega'}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}-\\epsilon'_{xx}\\right)E_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}} - \\frac{i\\,\\omega'}{c} \\, \\left({\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx}\\,E_{y}\\right)}{\\partial x}}-{\\frac {\\partial \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx}\\, E_{x}\\right)}{\\partial y}}\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = - \\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}-\\epsilon'_{xx}\\right)\\frac{i\\,\\omega'}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial E_{y}}{\\partial x}} + \\frac{i\\,\\omega'}{c} \\, \\epsilon'_{xx}\\left(rot \\vec E\\right)_z$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$rot\\,\\vec{E} = -\\frac{1}{c}\\frac{\\partial \\vec B}{\\partial t} = \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c}\\,\\mu'\\vec{H}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx}-\\epsilon'_{yy}\\right) \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial E_{y}}{\\partial x}} + \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, \\epsilon'_{xx}\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\mu' \\vec{H}\\right)_z$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "при условии недиагональности тензора магнитной проницаемости"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf{B} = \\left[ \\begin{array}{c} B_y \\\\ B_z \\\\ B_x \\end{array} \\right] = \n",
    "\\begin{pmatrix}\n",
    "\\mu'_{yy} & \\mu'_{yz} & 0 \\\\\n",
    "\\mu'_{zy} & \\mu'_{zz} & 0 \\\\\n",
    "0 & 0 & \\mu'_{xx}\n",
    "\\end{pmatrix} \n",
    "\\times\n",
    "\\left[ \\begin{array}{c} H_y \\\\ H_z \\\\ H_x \\end{array} \\right] =\n",
    "\\begin{pmatrix}\n",
    "\\mu'_{yy} H_y + \\mu'_{yz} H_z \\\\\n",
    "\\mu'_{zy} H_y + \\mu'_{zz} H_z \\\\\n",
    "\\mu'_{xx} H_x\n",
    "\\end{pmatrix} \n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx}-\\epsilon'_{yy}\\right) \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial  E_{y}}{\\partial x}} + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\, \\epsilon'_{xx}\\left(\\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \\mu'_{zy} H_y\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H} = grad\\,div\\,\\vec{H} - Laplasian\\,\\vec{H}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ Laplasian\\,\\vec{H} + rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H} - grad\\,div\\,\\vec{H} = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "для вакуума внутри резонатора ищем решение в виде\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\vec{H}(t) = \\vec{H}(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z}\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\vec{H} = \\vec{H}(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "подставляя в исходное уравнение приходим к обыкновенному дифференциальному уравнению\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}\\vec{H}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}\\vec{H}(x,y) + \\left(- {k'_z}^2\\right)\\,\\vec{H}(x,y) + rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H} - grad\\,div\\,\\vec{H} = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "покомпонентно"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_x}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_x}(x,y) + \\left( - {k'_z}^2\\right)\\,{H_x}(x,y)+ \\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_x - \\left(grad\\,div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_x = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_y}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_y}(x,y) + \\left(- {k'_z}^2\\right)\\,{H_y}(x,y)+ \\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_y - \\left(grad\\,div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_y = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\left(- {k'_z}^2\\right)\\,{H_z}(x,y)+ \\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z - \\left(grad\\,div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "подставляя $\\left(rot\\,rot\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx}-\\epsilon'_{yy}\\right) \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial  E_{y}}{\\partial x}} + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\, \\epsilon'_{xx}\\left(\\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \\mu'_{zy} H_y\\right)$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) - {k'_z}^2 \\,{H_z}(x,y)+ \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx}-\\epsilon'_{yy}\\right) \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial  E_{y}}{\\partial x}} + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\, \\epsilon'_{xx}\\left(\\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \\mu'_{zy} H_y\\right) - \\left(grad\\,div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Рассмотрим сейчас градиент дивергенции"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "ищем решение в виде позволяющем разделить переменные\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\vec{H}(t) = \\vec{H}(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z}\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\vec{H} = \\vec{H}(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$div = \\left(\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x} \\hat i + \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial y} \\hat j+ \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial z} \\hat k\\right) \\cdot$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$div\\,\\vec{H} = \\left(\\frac{\\partial H_x(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z}}{\\partial x} + \\frac{\\partial H_y(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z}}{\\partial y} + \\frac{\\partial H_z(x, y)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z}}{\\partial z}\\right)\\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t} $$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$div\\,\\vec{H} = \\left(\\frac{\\partial H_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} + \\frac{\\partial H_y(x, y)}{\\partial y} + i\\,K_z H_z(x, y)\\right)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z} \\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "выберем решение для которого поле не изменяется вдоль $y$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(grad \\, div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_x = \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}\\left(\\frac{\\partial H_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} +  i\\,K_z H_z(x, y)\\right)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z} \\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(grad \\, div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_x = \\left(\\frac{\\partial^2 H_x(x, y)}{\\partial x^2} +  i\\,K_z \\frac{\\partial H_z(x, y)}{\\partial x}\\right)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z} \\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(grad \\, div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_y = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(grad \\, div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = \\frac{\\partial}{\\partial z}\\left\\{\\left(\\frac{\\partial H_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} +  i\\,K_z H_z(x, y)\\right)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z}\\right\\} \\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(grad \\, div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = i \\,K_z\\left(\\frac{\\partial H_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} + i\\,K_z H_z(x, y)\\right)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z} \\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(grad \\, div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = \\left(i \\,K_z\\,\\frac{\\partial H_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} -\\,K_z^2 H_z(x, y)\\right)\\,e^{i\\,K_z\\,z} \\,e^{-i\\,\\omega\\,t}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Рассмотрим TE волну для которой $E_z = 0$.\n",
    "Для этой волны учитывая что $K_z = {k'_z}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Используя полученное ранее выражение для поперечных (по отношению к оси волновода $z$ ) компонент поля через продольные"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(\\frac{i \\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c} - \\frac{i\\,{k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}\\right) H_{x}= \\frac{1}{{k'_z} }\\frac {\\partial E_{z}}{\\partial y}-\\frac{c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(\\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}} - \\frac{i\\,\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{{k'_z} c}  \\right)E_y = \\frac{c}{\\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}} \\frac {\\partial E_{z}}{\\partial y}-\\frac{1}{{k'_z}}{\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Поскольку $E_z = 0$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(\\frac{i \\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c} - \\frac{i\\,{k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}\\right) H_{x}= -\\frac{c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(\\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}} - \\frac{i\\,\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{{k'_z} c}  \\right)E_y = -\\frac{1}{{k'_z}}{\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Находим выражение для поперечных компонент поля"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ H_{x}= -\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{i \\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c} - \\frac{i\\,{k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}\\right)}\\frac{c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ H_{x}= -\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{i \\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c^2} - \\frac{i\\,{k'_z}}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}\\right)}\\frac{1}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ H_{x}= -\\frac{1}{i\\left(\\frac{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{yy} {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c^2} - {k'_z}\\right)}{\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$E_y = -\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}} - \\frac{i\\,\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{{k'_z} c}  \\right){k'_z}}{\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$E_y = -\\frac{1}{i\\left(\\frac{{k'_z}^2 c}{\\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}} - \\frac{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{c}  \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial x}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "дифференцируя по x"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$ \\frac{\\partial H_{x}}{\\partial x} = -\\frac{1}{i \\left(\\frac{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{yy} {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c^2} - {k'_z}\\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 H_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial E_y}{\\partial x} = -\\frac{1}{i\\left(\\frac{{k'_z}^2 c}{\\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}} - \\frac{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{c}  \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 H_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "уравнения для недиагонального тензора"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{{k'_z} c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right) H_{y} = -\\frac{1}{{k'_z}}{\\frac {\\partial E_{z}}{\\partial x}} - \\frac{c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial y}}-\\frac{1}{ {k'_z} }\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c}{\\mu'}_{yz} H_z$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "сведутся к виду, учитывая  $E_z = 0$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{{k'_z} c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right) H_{y} = - \\frac{c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial y}}-\\frac{1}{ {k'_z} }\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c}{\\mu'}_{yz} H_z$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "откуда, выражая поперечные компоненты поля,"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$H_{y} = - \\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{{k'_z} c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)}\\left(\\frac{c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial y}}+\\frac{1}{ {k'_z} }\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c}{\\mu'}_{yz} H_z\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$H_{y} = - \\left(\\frac{c}{\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{{k'_z} c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right)\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial y}}+\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{{k'_z} c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{i {k'_z} c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right) {k'_z} }\\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c}{\\mu'}_{yz} H_z\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$H_{y} = - \\left(\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{i\\,\\omega^2}{{k'_z} c^2}{\\epsilon'}_{xx}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - i {k'_z} \\right)} {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial y}}+\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{\\omega}{ c}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{{k'_z}^2 c}{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right) }\\frac{\\omega}{c}{\\mu'}_{yz} H_z\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$H_{y} = - \\left(\\frac{1}{i\\,\\left(\\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2 {k'_z}}{\\epsilon'}_{xx}{\\mu'}_{yy}  - {k'_z} \\right)} {\\frac {\\partial H_{z}}{\\partial y}}+\\frac{{\\mu'}_{yz}}{\\left({\\mu'}_{yy}  - \\frac{c^2 {k'_z}^2 }{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{xx}} \\right) } H_z\\right)$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "подставляя в волновое уравнение"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) - {k'_z}^2 \\,{H_z}(x,y)+ \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx}-\\epsilon'_{yy}\\right) \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial  E_{y}}{\\partial x}} + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\, \\epsilon'_{xx}\\left(\\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \\mu'_{zy} H_y\\right) - \\left(grad\\,div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Учитывая что $\\left(grad \\, div\\,\\vec{H}\\right)_z = \\left(i \\,{k'_z}\\,\\frac{\\partial H_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} -\\,{k'_z}^2 H_z(x, y)\\right)$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) - {k'_z}^2 \\,{H_z}(x,y)+ \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx}-\\epsilon'_{yy}\\right) \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, {\\frac {\\partial  E_{y}}{\\partial x}} + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\, \\epsilon'_{xx}\\left(\\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \\mu'_{zy} H_y\\right) - \\left(i \\,{k'_z}\\,\\frac{\\partial H_x(x, y)}{\\partial x} -\\,{k'_z}^2 H_z(x, y)\\right) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Подставляя ранее найденные выражения для поперечных компонент магнитного поля в ТЕ волне"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) - {k'_z}^2 \\,{H_z}(x,y)+ \\left(\\epsilon'_{xx}-\\epsilon'_{yy}\\right) \\frac{i\\,\\omega}{c} \\, \\left(-\\frac{1}{i\\left(\\frac{{k'_z}^2 c}{\\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}} - \\frac{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{c}  \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 H_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}\\right) + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\, \\epsilon'_{xx}\\left(\\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \\mu'_{zy} H_y\\right) - \\left(i \\,{k'_z}\\,\\left(-\\frac{1}{i \\left(\\frac{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{yy} {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c^2} - {k'_z}\\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 H_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}\\right) -\\,{k'_z}^2 H_z(x, y)\\right) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": []
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}-\\epsilon'_{xx}\\right) \\frac{\\omega}{c} \\, \\left(\\frac{1}{\\left(\\frac{{k'_z}^2 c}{\\omega {\\mu'}_{xx}} - \\frac{\\omega {\\epsilon'}_{yy}}{c}  \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 H_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}\\right) + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\, \\epsilon'_{xx}\\left(\\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \\mu'_{zy} H_y\\right) - \\left(i \\,{k'_z}\\,\\left(-\\frac{1}{i \\left(\\frac{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{yy} {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c^2} - {k'_z}\\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 H_{z}}{\\partial x^2}}\\right) \\right) = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": []
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) +\n",
    "\\frac{\\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}-\\epsilon'_{xx}\\right)}{\\left(\\frac{{k'_z}^2 c^2}{\\omega^2 {\\mu'}_{xx}} - {\\epsilon'}_{yy}  \\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 H_{z}}{\\partial x^2}} + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\epsilon'_{xx} \\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \n",
    "\\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\epsilon'_{xx} \\mu'_{zy} H_y + \\frac{{k'_z}}{\\left(\\frac{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{yy} {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c^2} - {k'_z}\\right)}{\\frac {\\partial^2 H_{z}}{\\partial x^2}} = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": []
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(1 + \\frac{\\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}-\\epsilon'_{xx}\\right)}{\\left(\\frac{{k'_z}^2 c^2}{\\omega^2 {\\mu'}_{xx}} - {\\epsilon'}_{yy}  \\right)} + \\frac{{k'_z}}{\\left(\\frac{\\omega^2 {\\epsilon'}_{yy} {\\mu'}_{xx}}{{k'_z} c^2} - {k'_z}\\right)}\\right)\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {y})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\epsilon'_{xx} \\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \n",
    "\\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\epsilon'_{xx} \\mu'_{zy} H_y = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "поле не изменяется вдоль $y$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(1 + \\frac{\\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}-\\epsilon'_{xx}\\right)}{\\left(\\frac{{k'_z}^2 c^2}{\\omega^2 {\\mu'}_{xx}} - {\\epsilon'}_{yy}  \\right)} + \\frac{{k'_z}}{\\left(\\frac{\\omega^2 }{{k'_z} c^2}{\\epsilon'}_{yy} {\\mu'}_{xx} - {k'_z}\\right)}\\right)\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\epsilon'_{xx} \\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \n",
    "\\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\epsilon'_{xx} \\mu'_{zy} H_y = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(1  - \\frac{{k'_z}}{ {k'_z} - \\left(\\frac{\\omega^2 }{{k'_z} c^2}{\\epsilon'}_{yy} {\\mu'}_{xx} \\right)}- \\frac{\\left(\\epsilon'_{yy}-\\epsilon'_{xx}\\right)}{\\left({\\epsilon'}_{yy} - \\frac{{k'_z}^2 c^2}{\\omega^2 {\\mu'}_{xx}} \\right)}\\right)\\frac{\\partial^{2}}{(\\partial {x})^{2}}{H_z}(x,y) + \\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\epsilon'_{xx} \\mu'_{zz} {H}_z + \n",
    "\\frac{\\omega^2}{c^2} \\epsilon'_{xx} \\mu'_{zy} H_y = 0$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "подставляем $H_y$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
