   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$$\\left(grad \\, div\\,\\vec{E}\\right)_x = \\left(\\frac{\\partial^2 E_x(x, y)}{\\partial x^2} +  i\\,k'_z \\frac{\\partial E_z(x, y)}{\\partial x}\\right)$$"
