    "+ \\left(\\frac{\\epsilon - 1}{4 \\pi}\\vec{E}\\right)_y \\frac{\\partial E_y}{\\partial x}\n",
    "+ \\left(\\frac{\\epsilon - 1}{4 \\pi}\\vec{E}\\right)_z \\frac{\\partial E_z}{\\partial x}\n",
    "+ \\left[\\left(\\frac{\\epsilon - 1}{4 \\pi}\\vec{E}\\right) \\times rot \\vec{E}\\right]_x\n",
    "$$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "В случае диагональности тензора диэлектрической проницаемости\n",
    "\n",
